      *     画面ワークエリアにセット
            INITIALIZE                           Z01.
      *
            MOVE  SPA-Z01GMN-BS1LABEL             TO  Z01-BS1LABEL.
            MOVE  SPA-Z01GMN-BS1VALUE             TO  Z01-BS1VALUE.
      *
            MOVE  SPA-Z01GMN-SRYCD                TO  Z01-SRYCD.
