      *
            MOVE  SPA-Z01GMN-YUKOEDYMD            TO  Z01-YUKOEDYMD.
      *
            PERFORM VARYING IDXX    FROM    1   BY  1
                    UNTIL  IDXX     >       30
               MOVE  SPA-Z01GMN-TRENNUM(IDXX)      TO  Z01-TRENNUM 
                                                              (IDXX)
               MOVE  SPA-Z01GMN-TYUKOSTYMD(IDXX)   TO  Z01-TYUKOSTYMD
